<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 00:51:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>小米在中国汽车的艰难时期进军电动汽车领域</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-set-plunge-into-evs-tricky-time-china-autos-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国小米将于周四推出备受期待的电动汽车（EV），届时将公布定价并开始接受订单，这标志着这家电子公司进军汽车领域。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 23:02:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-set-plunge-into-evs-tricky-time-china-autos-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日元大坝已决口，但并未决堤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-27/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 21:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国新制裁针对朝鲜军事财政</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-north-korea-sanctions-target-individuals-russia-china-uae-based-firms-2024-03-27/</link><description>美国周三宣布对位于俄罗斯、中国和阿拉伯联合酋长国的六名个人和两个实体实施制裁，指责他们向朝鲜的武器计划提供资金。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-north-korea-sanctions-target-individuals-russia-china-uae-based-firms-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯公司开始在前 Stellantis 工厂生产雪铁龙</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russian-company-starts-citroen-production-former-stellantis-factory-2024-03-27/</link><description>俄罗斯汽车技术公司周三表示，已开始在莫斯科南部的一家工厂批量组装雪铁龙 C5 Aircross 车型，该工厂原属于 Stellantis 公司，这些汽车将于 5 月起在经销商处销售。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:10:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/russian-company-starts-citroen-production-former-stellantis-factory-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促盟国禁止公司为中国提供关键芯片制造工具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-is-urging-allies-bar-firms-servicing-key-chipmaking-tools-china-2024-03-27/</link><description>美国商务部官员周三表示，美国正在要求盟国阻止国内公司为中国客户提供某些芯片制造工具，同时加大力度限制中国的芯片制造能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:48:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-is-urging-allies-bar-firms-servicing-key-chipmaking-tools-china-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰首相在北京向中国习近平提出网络间谍问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/beijing-dutch-pm-raises-cyberespionage-with-chinas-xi-2024-03-27/</link><description>荷兰首相马克·吕特表示，他在周三与国家主席习近平的会谈中讨论了荷兰归咎于中国政府的网络间谍事件。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:15:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/beijing-dutch-pm-raises-cyberespionage-with-chinas-xi-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：第一量子高管与中国官员讨论投资和有争议的铜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/first-quantum-execs-discuss-investment-disputed-copper-with-chinese-officials-2024-03-27/</link><description>三名知情人士称，加拿大矿业公司第一量子矿业公司的高管上周会见了中国政府官员，讨论了涉及最大投资者江西铜业的融资和业务选择。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/first-quantum-execs-discuss-investment-disputed-copper-with-chinese-officials-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>智利矿业部长敦促SQM和天齐解决争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chiles-mining-minister-urges-sqm-tianqi-resolve-spat-2024-03-27/</link><description>智利矿业部长周三敦促智利矿商SQM和该公司大股东中国天齐锂业解决持续的争端，但没有介入他们的私人问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:08:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chiles-mining-minister-urges-sqm-tianqi-resolve-spat-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>驻菲律宾外国记者谴责中国涉嫌操纵视频</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-correspondents-philippines-condemn-china-over-claims-video-manipulation-2024-03-27/</link><description>驻马尼拉的外国记者周三驳斥了中国的说法，即菲律宾让记者篡改在南海补给任务期间拍摄的视频，使其看起来像“受害者”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:19:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/foreign-correspondents-philippines-condemn-china-over-claims-video-manipulation-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪的目标是年销量增长 20% - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicle-maker-byd-targets-20-jump-annual-sales-2024-03-27/</link><description>据三位知情人士透露，中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪设定了 2024 年销量目标 360 万辆，较去年破纪录的销量增长 20%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:15:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-vehicle-maker-byd-targets-20-jump-annual-sales-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>债券持有人团体“坚决反对”中国开发商世茂的债务重组提议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/bondholder-group-firmly-opposes-china-developer-shimaos-debt-revamp-proposal-2024-03-27/</link><description>违约的中国开发商世茂集团的一群主要债券持有人周三表示，“坚决反对”该公司重组115亿美元离岸债务的提议，在房地产行业危机不断加深的情况下，这给该公司的前景蒙上阴影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:01:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/bondholder-group-firmly-opposes-china-developer-shimaos-debt-revamp-proposal-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平告诉荷兰首相切断供应链将导致对抗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-tells-dutch-pm-cutting-supply-chains-would-lead-confrontation-2024-03-27/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国国家主席习近平周三对荷兰首相马克·吕特表示，制造技术壁垒、切断供应链只会导致分裂和对抗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-tells-dutch-pm-cutting-supply-chains-would-lead-confrontation-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>英格兰银行加强对私募股权和银行估值的审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-england-steps-up-scrutiny-private-equity-bank-valuations-2024-03-27/</link><description>路透伦敦3月27日 - 英国央行周三表示，正在更深入地研究不透明的私募股权行业带来的风险，以及为何英国主要银行的估值与国际同行相比“偏低”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:33:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-england-steps-up-scrutiny-private-equity-bank-valuations-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦军方和文职官员将调查造成中国公民死亡的爆炸事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-reviews-security-protocols-chinese-nationals-after-suicide-bombing-2024-03-27/</link><description>官员称，巴基斯坦总理周三呼吁军方和文职官员对导致五名中国工程师死亡的自杀式爆炸事件进行联合调查，同时审查其项目的安全安排。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:08:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistan-reviews-security-protocols-chinese-nationals-after-suicide-bombing-2024-03-27/</guid></item><item><title>由于需求不温不火，中国电动汽车制造商蔚来下调第一季度交付预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-nio-cuts-q1-deliveries-forecast-2024-03-27/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车周三下调了第一季度的交付预期，以应对中国需求放缓和价格战的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:38:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-nio-cuts-q1-deliveries-forecast-2024-03-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>